Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:01.38,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\fs66}要光明 要更多的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:03.80,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\fs66}要光明 要更多的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:07.72,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,向着顶点前进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:10.46,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\an8}Have an obsession for victory
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:12.96,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\an8}I'm proud of myself and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:15.69,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\an8}We must be the change we wish to see...
